A '''Doppler sensor array''' was an array of sensors keyed to the [[Wikipedia:Doppler effect|Doppler effect]]. At least one such sensor was found on [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor's]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] castle. However, this array was shattered by an erratically-[[Pilot/Legends|piloted]] [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']]. Any surviving remnants of the device were subsequently destroyed when the building collapsed.

